{
  "stem": "7546.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was a good thing, and we thought maybe we'll overcome it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Maybe we will come out unscratched.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "How little did I know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes. 5 o'clock, you couldn't walk out into the street, which immediately put a very heavy burden on us.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We couldn't go to the family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We couldn't see the family.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if you did walk out into the street, you took a chance of being caught by the Germans for manual labor.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they were catching people in the middle of the street, and in some cases, you did work that was unnecessary.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Like they gave you a toothbrush to clean the toilet, an outhouse, to sweep the floor with a toothbrush, or to carry stones.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just to make us feel Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To put the shame on us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, well, it was strictly humiliation, of course.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got caught three times.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Three times.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I got caught to work, and that's where the story actually begins.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my father decided that my brother and I should not stay here any longer, since a lot of people were going towards the Russian border and crossing into the Soviet Union.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "My father decided that my brother and I should leave Poland and go into the Russian border and cross into Russia, which we did.",
      "word_count": 24
    }
  ],
